---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
import ContactBox from '../components/ContactBox.astro';
import Button from '../components/extra/button.astro';

import HouseOpen from "../assets/videos/WPS-Hero_video.mp4";
import Broward from "../assets/images/waterfront_fort_lauderdale.png";
import HandShake from "../assets/images/shaking_hands.png";
import Phone from "../assets/images/phone_call.png";
import Relax from "../assets/images/relax.png";
---

<Layout title="Whiddon Property Solutions">
	<header class="hero container">
		<video autoplay muted loop id="houseopen">
			<source src={HouseOpen} type="video/mp4">
		</video>
		<div class="overlay"></div>
		<div class="hero-content hero_text_shadow" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-easing="ease-out-back" data-aos-duration="2000" data-aos-delay="0">
			<h4 class="baskervville-regular">WHIDDON PROPERTY SOLUTIONS</h4>
			<p>We offer a white-glove experience designed to address and resolve issues such as</p>
			<ul class="inline word-alts">
				<li>code violations</li>
				<li>Open Permits/General Permitting</li>
				<li>Remodeling/Construction</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Serving Broward, Miami-Dade, and Palm Beach County</p>
			<div class="d-none d-md-block">
				<Button
					link="/Contact"
					text="Work With Us"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="d-md-none">
				<Button
					link="tel:9546497315"
					text="Work With Us"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="text_content_background">
		<div class="container py-3">
			<h4 class="baskervville-regular text-center">Why Choose Whiddon Property Solutions?</h4>

			<div class="py-3">
				<p class="text-center">You may ask why Whiddon Property Solutions was started? It all began with our first flip home! We quickly learned the hard way about the importance of permits and following code when performing work and renovations on an investment property. The city of Fort Lauderdale has become more and more aggressive over the last couple of years, and is very serious about compliance. Our oversight created major hurdles when it came time to sell and finding a willing buyer. Instead of letting it hold us back, we turned this challenge into our mission: helping investors and homeowners navigate the complexities of property and code violations, and turning them into solutions. Here’s to learning from our mistakes and building a better way forward! </p>
			</div>

			<div class="row align-items-center py-3 flex-column flex-md-row" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="0">
				<div class="col-md-5 col image_box">
					<Image src={Broward} alt="Broward Counties Beautiful Waterfront" class="left_shadow"/>
				</div>
				<p class="col-md-7 col text-center">Whiddon Property Solutions is a premier concierge service specializing in comprehensive solutions and management of property-related challenges for homeowners and property owners in the Broward County of South Florida.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="row align-items-center flex-column flex-md-row-reverse py-3" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="0">
				<div class="col-md-5 col image_box">
					<Image src={HandShake} alt="We take care of the work" class="right_shadow"/>
				</div>
				<p class="col-md-7 col text-center">Our dedicated team will take on the heavy lifting by overseeing all interactions with city workers, clerks, inspectors, and other officials, all the way until each case is closed and resolved to the property owner’s satisfaction. We ensure that every necessary document and form is meticulously managed, signed, and submitted, alleviating the burden from our clients and expediting the resolution process.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="row align-items-center py-3 flex-column flex-md-row" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="0">
				<div class="col-md-5 col image_box">
					<Image src={Phone} alt="Customer Service" class="left_shadow"/>
				</div>
				<p class="col-md-7 col text-center">
					We pride ourselves on our around-the-clock customer service, commitment to timely resolutions, and transparency by providing regular updates and maintaining open lines of communication to ensure that our clients are always informed about the status of their property.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="row align-items-center flex-column flex-md-row-reverse py-3" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="0">
				<div class="col-md-5 col image_box">
					<Image src={Relax} alt="Relax while we do the work" class="right_shadow"/>
				</div>
				<p class="col-md-7 col text-center">
					Serving all of Broward County, Whiddon Property Solutions is your trusted partner for seamless property management and compliance, allowing you to focus on what matters most while we handle the intricacies of property care.</p>
			</div>

			<p class="text-center">Our General Contracting License : LIC# CGC1532274</p>

			<ContactBox
				text="Need Help? Contact Us Today for a Free Consultation."
			/>
		</div>

	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	header {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		/* width: 800px; */
		/* max-width: calc(100% - 2rem); */
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		height: 100vh;
	}
	#houseopen {
		position: absolute;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		min-width: 100%;
		min-height: 100%;
	}
	.hero-content {
		display: grid;
		place-content: center;
		height: 100vh;
		width: 100%;
		z-index: 10;
		position: relative;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.home_content {
		background-size: cover;
	}
	.image_box img{
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}
</style>
